SELECT\
	*\
FROM `smarty_framework`.`query_menus`\
WHERE\
	(`subdomain_id`=27 OR `subdomain_id`=0)\
	AND `is_active`='Y'\
ORDER BY\
	menu_context,\
	sink_weight,\
	menu_text\
;
